channel.title: Top of the line bots?
channel.description:
I'm considering getting back into Runescape botting, so my question is this. What are the best quality bots out there these days? And I don't just mean free ones, but those that require a payment as well.
By quality I mean most efficient, and least detectable. The latter being the most important.
